    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Generate quotes with HTTP / REST API and Airtable in real time\n\n**Pattern:** Document Generation · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nGenerate quotes with HTTP / REST API and Airtable in real time. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual invoices is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nOn Telegram Event → Gather API Numbers → Blend Sources → Roll Up KPIs → Compose HTML Report → Send Report via Telegram → Save Execution Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to document generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating invoices in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Telegram bot token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "933fc47e-e6e1-abf3-f088-115041cb854a",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your invoices process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.",
        "width": 360,
        "height": 260,
        "color": 4
      },
